  "configurar-el-enrutamiento-en-server-2012": "<p style=\"background-color: white; color: #373737; cursor: url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.ani\"), url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.png\"), auto; font-family: \"Times New Roman\", Times, FreeSerif, serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red; cursor: url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.ani\"), url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.png\"), auto;\"><b style=\"cursor: url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.ani\"), url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.png\"), auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">IMPORTANTE</span></b></span></p><h3 style=\"background-color: white; color: #373737; cursor: url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.ani\"), url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.png\"), auto; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet; font-size: medium;\"><i>La configuración es la siguiente:</i></span></h3><p style=\"background-color: white; color: #373737; cursor: url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.ani\"), url(\"https://ani.cursors-4u.net/cursors/cur-13/cur1162.png\"), auto; font-size: 14.85px; text-align: center;\"></p><ul style=\"text-align: left;\"><li><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet;\"><i><b>DHCP:</b> El Gateway debe ser la IP del server, en mi caso 192.168.2.1</i></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet;\"><i><b>WAN:</b> Añadir un adaptador en Bridge al server para que este tenga <span style=\"background-color: #fce5cd;\"><u>acceso</u></span> a la red de redes(<span style=\"background-color: #fce5cd;\"><u>Internet</u></span>)</i></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet;\"><i><b>Reenviadores:</b> Se debe añadir dos reenviadores, que son los siguientes:</i></span></li><ul><ul><ul></ul><li><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet;\"><i>8.8.8.8</i></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet;\"><i>8.8.4.4</i></span></li></ul></ul></ul><div><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet;\"><i><br /></i></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: trebuchet;\"><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"BLOG_video_class\" height=\"285\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KqLgwxHqq3s\" width=\"502\" youtube-src-id=\"KqLgwxHqq3s\"></iframe></div><br /><i><br /></i></span></div><p></p>",
